originalText: I dreamt I was flying over a giant library floating above the clouds. Each book glowed and whispered names of ancient people. I picked one book up, and suddenly found myself inside a desert, standing at the feet of a massive, transparent hourglass where sand was flowing upwards. A child stood beside it, offering me a key made of stars.
